{"tid":611643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌媽駕車剷行人路撼食肆外牆　9歲子受驚不適","createTime":"2018-03-31T08:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T09:03:10.000Z","uid":147194,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ab5e516b9256b0c64dbea3442eeeafcb8e8a20","tid":611643,"uid":147194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180331/photo/bkn-20180331133731128-0331_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180331160530\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180331%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180331133731128-0331_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180331160530&h=3d955b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛頭角發生私家車剷上行人路驚險交通意外。下午近1時，姓馮(37歲)<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">女子</span></span>載着9歲姓林兒子，駕駛掛着「P」牌的七人車，沿觀塘道東行，駛至得寶花園對開準備左轉入彩雲道時，突失控越過對面線，撞毀近5米長鐵欄後再剷上行人路，猛撼得寶商場一間食肆外牆始停下，幸未撞及途人。私家車車頭嚴重損毀，漏出滿地偈油，警員其後用木糠將其遮蓋以便清理。林童事後疑受驚感不適，由到場救護車送院。警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n根據運輸署資料顯示，涉事七人車由一間公司持有，於去年4月以約35萬港元購入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東網<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180331/bkn-20180331133731128-0331_00822_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180331%2Fbkn-20180331133731128-0331_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=NGHX1sD0FsocOWVjFLgZz5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c15fc86e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180331/bkn-20180331133731128-0331_00822_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"ee538c7a8a2e6543e2edbc42a5f7a23e366188e2","tid":611643,"uid":147194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed913aa757b0ecf3fa9cf079fdea8c2fa36bef5","tid":611643,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"樓主性別歧視<img src=\"/a